<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<add>hochwirdikeit</add> nehst von <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Freyen,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers, und der sache wegen, als er
                        mit <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> der ewren genant Jacob Cramer czu Pettaw
                        gesessen cze handeln hat, <add><expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan></add> darümb auch der
                                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden kümt.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan></add>
<expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        willigen dinste willen darynne <add>wollet</add>
<expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen, also daz er
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> gnaden darynne genysse,
                                    <add><expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> er maint, daz im gar ungütlich
                                    <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                            geschehe</add>, als etc. Das wöllen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>divis<ex>ionem</ex></expan>
<expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>lo<ex>rum.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
